    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A dashboard-style, single-page application. The structure moves from a high-level summary (Hero, Key Metrics) to a detailed exploration of The Opportunity (Market), The Solution (Services), The Plan (Operations), and finally a SWOT/Risk analysis. This non-linear, thematic structure allows users to quickly grasp the key takeaways and then dive into specific areas of interest, which is more engaging and user-friendly than a linear report. Navigation will be handled by a sticky header and interactive cards. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: Key stats (Investment, Profitability) are presented as dynamic cards for quick information. A Chart.js donut chart visualizes the target market split for comparison. The competitive landscape and team growth phases are represented using custom HTML/CSS diagrams for better organization and visual flow. An interactive SWOT-like grid synthesizes Pros, Cons, and Risks. This approach was chosen to transform dense text into scannable, engaging visual elements, enhancing user understanding and retention. All visualizations use Canvas or HTML/CSS, adhering to the NO SVG/Mermaid constraint. -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
